  "title": "Drug-induced psychosis associated with albendazole-ivermectin combination therapy.",
  "abstract": "We report a case that experienced psychosis after combination therapy of albendazole and ivermectin. This case report represents the first report of psychosis caused by this combination therapy and its treatment with clonazepam.",
